<br>
I’m curious whether most people agree if it’s within the RTA’s charter to attempt to implement a punishment or punitive measures against a guild (in this case) or an individual?  I think the answer should be no, it is not within the RTA’s charter to attempt to determine a “suitable” penalty.<br>
<br>
